snippet.title: Virtual Hunter | Pheasant Update Overview
snippet.description:
Virtual Hunters new major update is now released! In this massive patch we are adding pheasants, new features, graphical improvements, quality of life improvements and a lot of other improvements and fixes!

Read the full patch notes: https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1549850/view/3253308604336019928

Get the game from Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1549850/Virtual_Hunter

Join our Discord server: https://discord.gg/gGmSAA8Prd
Follow us on Facebook: https://bit.ly/3DDP0QV
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/VirtualHunterVR
Website: http://virtualhuntervr.com

#virtualhuntervr #virtualreality #hunting
